room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: What a fun night and something different to do. We did the Apartment with 28 seconds to spare. Such a rush!

room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We had a blast escaping The Apartment Room. Would love to try the other rooms. Well done!

room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: Absolutely loved it. Went to celebrate my birthday and did the Apartment room. So much fun. I want to do another one.

room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We unfortunately didn't escape the Apartment but we were soooooo close! Another 3 minutes and we would've been out! It was exhilarating and lots of fun! We're going back to do the others!

room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: It was a lot of fun! We did "the Apartment". The hints were subtle but helpful and also entertaining! Definitely plan to do the other two rooms. Staff was nice, fun and helpful!
